As one would expect, not all your life revolves around college. Certainly, your personal habits and characteristics are, or can be, a reflection of those of the country. For this reason they are very important because they will give yo
ur British partners first hand information about the people of a country they hardly know.
\par 
\par Therein lies the task: to learn to know each other better in order to widen horizons, to get along better and--why not?--to appreciate each other more.
\par 
